item.title: OpenCv开发中所遇到的问题备忘
item.description: OpenCv开发中所遇到的问题备忘 1.qt库冲突的问题： 1 2 3 You might be loading two sets of Qt binaries into the same process. Check that all plugins are compiled against the right Qt binaries. Export DYLD_PRINT_LIBRARIES=1 and check that only one set of binaries are being loaded. QObject::moveToThread: Current
